*.key

# Stripe Keys & Secrets (PROTECTED)
# Never commit live OR test Stripe keys!
# CRITICAL: All Stripe keys are protected - test and live keys
*sk_live_*
*sk_test_*
*pk_live_*
*pk_test_*
*whsec_*
*stripe*.key
*stripe*.secret
*stripe*.env
*STRIPE_KEYS*.md
