*stripe-keys*.md
*stripe-keys*.txt
*STRIPE_KEY*.md
*STRIPE_KEY*.txt
STRIPE_KEY_ADDED.md
# Environment variables containing Stripe keys
*STRIPE_SECRET_KEY*
*STRIPE_TEST_SECRET_KEY*
*STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY*
*STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET*
# Additional protection: Any file containing Stripe key patterns
*/*stripe*key*
*/*STRIPE*KEY*

